  "prompt": "How do I recover a Yahoo hacked email address?",
  "response": "To recover a Yahoo email account that has been hacked, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Secure Your Account:**\n   - Go to the Yahoo sign-in page and click on \"Trouble signing in?\"\n   - Choose the option to reset your password. You may need to answer security questions or use a recovery email or phone number to verify your identity.\n   - Set a new, strong password. Make sure it's different from any previous passwords and includes a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols.\n\n2. **Review Account Activity:**\n   - Once you regain access, go to the \"Account Info\" section and review recent activity.\n   - Look for any unfamiliar devices or locations that accessed your account and remove them.\n\n3. **Enable Two-Factor Authentication (2FA):**\n   - Go to the \"Account Security\" section.\n   - Enable two-factor authentication to add an extra layer of security. This will require a code sent to your phone or an authenticator app whenever you sign in from a new device.\n\n4. **Update Security Questions and Recovery Information:**\n   - Make sure your security questions and answers are up to date and secure.\n   - Update your recovery email address and phone number to ensure you can regain access if your account is compromised again.\n\n5. **Scan for Malware:**\n   - Run a full system scan on your computer and any devices you use to access your Yahoo account to check for malware or viruses that may have contributed to the hack.\n\n6. **Change Passwords for Other Accounts:**\n   - If you used the same password for other accounts, change those passwords immediately to prevent further breaches.\n\n7. **Contact Yahoo Support:**\n   - If you encounter any issues during the recovery process, contact Yahoo Customer Care for further assistance.\n\n8. **Monitor Your Account:**\n   - Keep an eye on your account for any suspicious activity in the future and report any issues to Yahoo immediately.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to recover your hacked Yahoo email account and secure it against future attacks.",
